1758→    Let $A$ be a ring. Denote by $S(A)$ the set of finite subsets of faithfully flat étale $A$-algebras.
1759→    We call the $A$-algebra $T(A) = \colim_{E \in S(A)} \bigotimes_{B \in E} B$ the \emph{étale precontraction} of
1760→    $A$.
